  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA15">
<l>mutalāvār mūvarē yammūva ruḷḷu</l>
<l>mutalāvāṉ mūrinīr vaṇṇaṉ – mutalāya</l>
<l>nallā ṉaruḷallā ṉāmanīr vaiyakattup</l>
<l>pallā raruḷum paḻutu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Just the Three will be first. Among those three,</l>
<l>the one with the colour of mighty water is the first. Except for the grace</l>
<l>of the good one who is the first, in the world [surrounded by] ample waters,</l>
<l>vain [are] the graces of many.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
